title: Programming Quotes
metadesc: Let's see some programming quotes that maybe will make you ponder why programming is so good!
content:
Hehe guys! Welcome to another post. Let's read some programming quotes that will make your day good!

 

1) Programming is 10% writing code and 90% understanding why it's not working.

 

2) "Code is like humor. When you have to explain it, it's bad"

 

- Cory House.

 

3) "Always code as if the guy who ends up maintaining your code will be a violent psychopath who knows where you live"

 

- John woods

 

4) "A good programmer is someone who always looks both ways before crossing a one-way street."

 

-Doug Linder

 

5) Coding is my warmup and debugging is my cardio

 

6) "Java is to JavaScript as ham is to hamster"

 

-Jeremy keith.

 

7) Developer : An organism that converts coffee into code.

 

That's it guys, for this post. Thank you so much for sparing your time to read this post. Have a nice day!
